<subSubSection id="C36B652A81DCFF70FF31FE52FDB0FD5E" pageId="243" pageNumber="244" type="distribution">
<paragraph id="8BCE36A181DCFF70FF31FE52FDFDFDF2" blockId="243.[136,1452,410,653]" pageId="243" pageNumber="244">
<emphasis id="B905EAB381DCFF70FF31FE52FEC6FE2E" bold="true" box="[189,373,482,508]" pageId="243" pageNumber="244">Distribution:—</emphasis>
<collectingCountry id="F366763181DCFF70FEF9FE53FE57FE2F" box="[373,484,483,509]" name="Myanmar" pageId="243" pageNumber="244">Myanmar</collectingCountry>
, 
<collectingCountry id="F366763181DCFF70FE7AFE52FDEFFE2E" box="[502,604,482,508]" name="Thailand" pageId="243" pageNumber="244">Thailand</collectingCountry>
, Indochina, southwestern and southern 
<collectingCountry id="F366763181DCFF70FBB3FE52FB36FE2E" box="[1087,1157,482,508]" name="China" pageId="243" pageNumber="244">China</collectingCountry>
, 
<collectingCountry id="F366763181DCFF70FB1BFE52FB5FFE2E" box="[1175,1260,482,508]" name="Taiwan" pageId="243" pageNumber="244">Taiwan</collectingCountry>
, 
<collectingCountry id="F366763181DCFF70FB73FE53FAF1FE2F" box="[1279,1346,483,509]" name="Japan" pageId="243" pageNumber="244">Japan</collectingCountry>
, western 
<collectingCountry id="F366763181DCFF70FF04FDB6FF52FDF2" box="[136,225,518,544]" name="Malaysia" pageId="243" pageNumber="244">Malesia</collectingCountry>
and possibly northeastern 
<collectingCountry id="F366763181DCFF70FD81FDB6FDF9FDF2" box="[525,586,518,544]" name="India" pageId="243" pageNumber="244">India</collectingCountry>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8BCE36A181DCFF70FF31FD9AFDB0FD5E" blockId="243.[136,1452,410,653]" pageId="243" pageNumber="244">
<emphasis id="B905EAB381DCFF70FF31FD9AFEA8FD96" bold="true" box="[189,283,554,580]" pageId="243" pageNumber="244">Note:—</emphasis>
Taxonomic studies by Ormerod (2018: 274) clearly indicated that this name has been misapplied outside of 
<collectingCountry id="F366763181DCFF70FF2AFDFEFEBEFDBA" box="[166,269,590,616]" name="Malaysia" pageId="243" pageNumber="244">Malaysia</collectingCountry>
and 
<collectingCountry id="F366763181DCFF70FECDFDFEFE05FDBA" box="[321,438,590,616]" name="Singapore" pageId="243" pageNumber="244">Singapore</collectingCountry>
. The identity of 
<collectingCountry id="F366763181DCFF70FDE6FDFFFD64FDBB" box="[618,727,591,617]" name="Myanmar" pageId="243" pageNumber="244">Myanmar</collectingCountry>
material (which is likely a different taxon) is an issue the authors hope to take up in the near future.
</paragraph>
